    • guessReaderForInput

      public static Reader guessReaderForInput​(String file_name) throws IOException
      Sets an input reader by parsing the file path: if it looks like an URL, a URL connection is initiated; if it ends with gz, then it is uncompressed on the fly.
      Parameters:
      file_name - URL or file path name
      Returns:
      reader for the (possibly uncompressed file content)
      Throws:
      IOException - if URL access fails, or the file cannot be opened for reading
